<h2>How to use?</h2>
<h3>Search for a Category</h3>
<p> Try for using {host}/bcjp-api/2015?category=3 </p>
<h3>Search for a Subcategory</h3>
<p> Try for using {host}/bcjp-api/2015?subcategory=3C </p>
